{"tid":411123,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"老豆懷疑有外遇，被老母發現，點勸交？","createTime":"2017-09-23T14:07:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T06:01:10.000Z","uid":67020,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bbbb31c9a454c695c85976189d23f73d40ce3673","tid":411123,"uid":67020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:07:01.000Z","msg":"如題，<br />\n我老豆一直話冇野，<br />\n我老母而家好火，<br />\n暫時雙方冷戰緊，<br />\n而我就唔想頭家散，<br />\n但我又唔識點講野，點勸？<br />\n有冇過來人分享下經驗？<br />\n我係家中獨子，<br />\n有兄弟姊妹都叫有人分擔下，唉"},{"pid":"793c598b92fac2213092d8377ba2bd6db9189785","tid":411123,"uid":115778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:08:19.000Z","msg":"買頂帽畀老竇"},{"pid":"c776b32a4355c3dc3444c6af80ea1b5c4d53aa95","tid":411123,"uid":115778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:08:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買頂帽畀老竇</blockquote><br />\n叫佢畀老母"},{"pid":"fde34332e178f05b514d548786a2c953bcb80053","tid":411123,"uid":120317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:14:20.000Z","msg":"過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同你一樣獨仔，首先你幾大先？<br />\n如果你仲讀緊書嘅兩老未必想你插咀"},{"pid":"314e23d29edb1260c0d312e83aebe872bef6e9f8","tid":411123,"uid":67020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:17:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過來人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同你一樣獨仔，首先你幾大先？<br />\n如果你仲讀緊書嘅兩老未必想你插咀</blockquote><br />\n仲讀緊書，大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你而家屋企咩環境？<br />\n我一直視家為第一，唉"},{"pid":"c24d9e8307eba0ff859fc1009b4e678a00402ff2","tid":411123,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:20:15.000Z","msg":"屌左條女入自己數"},{"pid":"8e1d43121301c312e8c4a9fb1c9fe7c41f05dde9","tid":411123,"uid":67020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T14:24:05.000Z","msg":"認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hk